*Note: Expert witness work adds AU$100K-500K+ annually for Directors/Partners (day rates AU$5K-15K). PhD qualifications command 20-30% premium. Economics consulting pays ~70-80% of MBB compensation with significantly better work-life balance (45-55 vs 60-70 hour weeks).*

